forgotten the last travesty?

13
00:02:00,250 --> 00:02:02,041
All right everybody,
take your seats.

14
00:02:02,125 --> 00:02:04,250
I want you to meet
our new transfer student.

15
00:02:04,333 --> 00:02:05,583
Come on in.

16
00:02:08,666 --> 00:02:10,791
Go ahead and introduce yourself.

17
00:02:13,875 --> 00:02:15,125
I'm Aren Kuboyasu.

18
00:02:15,208 --> 00:02:17,458
I moved here from
Ibaraki Prefecture-- Uh!

19
00:02:17,541 --> 00:02:19,375
Sorry, old habit!
Forget I just did that!

20
00:02:19,458 --> 00:02:21,333
Hey, nice to meet you, Kuboyasu!

21
00:02:21,416 --> 00:02:22,500
Oh, cool.

22
00:02:22,583 --> 00:02:24,250
'Sup, homies?

23
00:02:24,333 --> 00:02:25,541
[BOY STUDENT I]
"'Sup, homies"?

24
00:02:25,625 --> 00:02:26,958
[BOY STUDENT J laughs]
Welcome!

25
00:02:27,041 --> 00:02:29,041
The new kid seems like
a pretty interesting guy, huh?

26
00:02:29,125 --> 00:02:30,916
[SAIKI] If only he
was just "interesting."

27
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,166
[KUBOYASU grunts]

28
00:02:33,958 --> 00:02:35,541
Damn it, that was too close.

29
00:02:35,625 --> 00:02:37,708
They almost found me out there.

30
00:02:37,791 --> 00:02:40,000
Ain't easy acting like
a goody two-shoes.

31
00:02:40,083 --> 00:02:42,541
[KUBOYASU] I'm a former punk,
and my folks were punks, too.

32
00:02:42,625 --> 00:02:44,125
My old man was head
of a biker gang,

33
00:02:44,208 --> 00:02:45,291
and Mom led a women's gang.

34
00:02:45,375 --> 00:02:46,791
Course I'd follow
in their footsteps.

35
00:02:46,875 --> 00:02:47,791
Grow my hair out.

36
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:49,416
In third grade,
I ruled my school.

37
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,416
One time, this lug
pulled out my hair.

38
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:54,291
Thought I was done for,
but I turned the tables on him.

39
00:02:54,375 --> 00:02:55,958
All through high school,
I kept fighting

40
00:02:56,041 --> 00:02:57,875
and kept growing my hair,
until eventually,

41
00:02:57,958 --> 00:03:00,791
I had my own gang and
my hair touched the ground.

42
00:03:00,875 --> 00:03:02,458
I wasn't really thinkin'
straight back then.

43
00:03:02,541 --> 00:03:05,208
I wouldn't say
I regret those days,

44
00:03:05,291 --> 00:03:08,250
but I did get sick of stepping
on my own hair all the time.

45
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:10,875
Now that I've changed schools,
my punk days are behind me.

46
00:03:10,958 --> 00:03:12,541
I ain't gotta fight no more.

47
00:03:12,625 --> 00:03:14,750
I'ma study hard and
live the straight and narrow.

48
00:03:14,833 --> 00:03:16,333
Just you watch!

49
00:03:16,416 --> 00:03:19,541
And if anyone gets in my way,
I'll beat the crap out of 'em!

50
00:03:19,625 --> 00:03:21,125
[SAIKI]
So much for not fighting.

51
00:03:21,208 --> 00:03:24,125
Everyone has a past and secrets
they wanna keep to themselves.

52
00:03:24,208 --> 00:03:25,291
I have no problem with that,

53
00:03:25,375 --> 00:03:27,041
but people don't just
change over night.

54
00:03:27,125 --> 00:03:28,916
If he causes trouble
at our school,

55
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,875
I'll get him transferred.

56
00:03:30,958 --> 00:03:32,375
[KUBOYASU]
Hmm?

57
00:03:32,458 --> 00:03:33,541
[BOY STUDENT L] Oh, he must
be the new transfer student.

58
00:03:33,625 --> 00:03:36,458
