68
00:03:53,208 --> 00:03:55,000
[SAIKI] Don't think many
delinquents would either.

69
00:03:55,083 --> 00:03:55,916
[KUBOYASU]
I can't do anything!

70
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,375
It's like I'm tied to a leash!

71
00:03:57,458 --> 00:03:59,208
[SAIKI] Feels that way 'cause
you were running wild.

72
00:03:59,291 --> 00:04:00,916
[NENDOU]
Hey, new kid!

73
00:04:02,583 --> 00:04:04,041
[SAIKI]
What's with all the punctuation?

74
00:04:04,125 --> 00:04:06,291
[KUBOYASU]
Huh? Who the hell is this guy?

75
00:04:06,375 --> 00:04:09,166
Looks like a punk.
And a real tough one at that.

76
00:04:09,250 --> 00:04:12,791
All right. Guess
I got some time to kill.

77
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:16,666
[KUBOYASU] No way! I ain't
throwing down with you, homes!

78
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,166
