I've mellowed out now,

89
00:04:33,291 --> 00:04:35,166
but I used to do some pretty
crazy stuff back in the day.

90
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:37,833
[KUBOYASU] He wants to tell war
stories? This oughta be good.

91
00:04:37,916 --> 00:04:39,708
