The worst thing that I ever did

93
00:04:41,208 --> 00:04:43,625
was chase mosquitoes
around with a mosquito coil.

94
00:04:43,708 --> 00:04:47,166
Though another time I did eat a
whole watermelon all by myself.

95
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,583
