99
00:04:52,708 --> 00:04:53,958
[KUBOYASU growls]

100
00:04:54,041 --> 00:04:55,666
[KUBOYASU] Man, that punk
wannabe pisses me off!

101
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:58,083
The old me woulda torn him
to shreds in two seconds!

102
00:04:58,166 --> 00:04:59,500
Damn it!

103
00:04:59,583 --> 00:05:01,958
Dudes who brag about how
bad they are are just posers.

104
00:05:02,041 --> 00:05:03,666
I should teach him
that personally.

105
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,666
[SAIKI] Do that and
you'll be outed as a punk.

106
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:07,750
[KUBOYASU] 'Least I didn't
start a fight back there.

107
00:05:07,833 --> 00:05:09,625
[SAIKI]
That's true. I was impressed.

108
00:05:09,708 --> 00:05:11,500
[KUBOYASU] A real man
picks a course of action

109
00:05:11,583 --> 00:05:13,333
and commits to it.

110
00:05:13,416 --> 00:05:14,958
