111
00:05:15,041 --> 00:05:16,875
Wait, no! Please don't hurt me!

112
00:05:16,958 --> 00:05:19,791
Hey what are you
lookin' at? Beat it!

113
00:05:19,875 --> 00:05:21,208
Now, let's hurry up.

114
00:05:21,291 --> 00:05:23,083
I'll give you whatever you want!

115
