118
00:05:26,875 --> 00:05:30,000
Act like trash in front of me,
you get treated like trash!

119
00:05:30,083 --> 00:05:31,375
I'll show you what's up, homey!

120
00:05:31,458 --> 00:05:33,000
[KONGOU screams]

121
00:05:33,083 --> 00:05:35,125
[SAIKI] Like I said, people
don't change over night.

122
00:05:35,208 --> 00:05:36,791
You didn't see nothin'.
You got that?

123
00:05:36,875 --> 00:05:38,541
Got it, please don't hurt me!

124
00:05:38,625 --> 00:05:41,166
[SAIKI] Well, guess
I can overlook this one.

125
00:05:47,708 --> 00:05:49,250
[KUBOYASU] It's been
a week since I transferred

126
00:05:49,333 --> 00:05:53,083
to this school. So far, no one's
figured out I'm a former punk.

127
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:55,041
But then why don't
I have any friends yet?

128
00:05:55,125 --> 00:05:57,083
Before, it was as simple
as beating up guys

129
00:05:57,166 --> 00:05:57,916
who tried to fight me.

130
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,041
