ain't doin' me any good.

133
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:04,708
Gotta go talk.

134
00:06:04,791 --> 00:06:08,125
Well, he's out. I can't
hang with another punk.

135
00:06:08,208 --> 00:06:10,833
His face ticks me off. Might
punch him without thinkin'.

136
00:06:10,916 --> 00:06:11,958
Hmm?

137
00:06:12,041 --> 00:06:14,083
That guy could work.
His name's, uh...

138
00:06:14,166 --> 00:06:15,291
Eh, can't remember.

139
00:06:15,375 --> 00:06:17,583
Whatever. I'll give
this weakling a shot.

140
00:06:17,666 --> 00:06:19,166
Yo, I'm Kuboyasu.
How's it goin'?

141
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,083
[SAIKI]
Wanna throw down, punk?

142
00:06:21,166 --> 00:06:22,625
[KUBOYASU] So, this
one guy shot this other guy,

143
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:24,375
breaking the pledge of
brotherhood between them...

144
00:06:24,458 --> 00:06:25,833
[SAIKI] What a pain.
I've been ignoring him,

145
00:06:25,916 --> 00:06:27,208
but he just keeps
going on and on

146
00:06:27,291 --> 00:06:29,250
about some dumb
yakuza movie he saw.

147
00:06:29,333 --> 00:06:32,875
And he's terrible at summaries.
How many guys are there?

148
00:06:32,958 --> 00:06:34,375
Enough.

149
00:06:34,458 --> 00:06:36,541
I hate to use this technique,
but it's time to deploy...

150
00:06:36,625 --> 00:06:38,541
...my annoyed face.

151
00:06:38,625 --> 00:06:39,750
Huh?!

152
00:06:39,833 --> 00:06:40,833
[SAIKI] See? You don't
need psychic powers

153
00:06:40,916 --> 00:06:41,625
to drive people away.

154
00:06:41,708 --> 00:06:43,916
Oh. All right, See ya.

155
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,833
[KUBOYASU growls]
How dare that goody-goody

156
00:06:45,916 --> 00:06:48,625
