for sheep waiting on...

160
00:06:55,375 --> 00:06:56,625
[KUBOYASU]
This is hopeless.

161
00:06:56,708 --> 00:06:59,291
I can't understand a word
these normal people say!

162
00:06:59,375 --> 00:07:02,208
[SAIKI] Yeah, there's nothing
normal about that guy.

163
