complete the "Grand Cross"!

165
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,250
[KUBOYASU] "Grand Cross"?
I've heard of that!

166
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:09,958
[KUBOYASU]
Oh, right! The legendary group!

167
00:07:10,041 --> 00:07:11,250
[KAIDOU]
