169
00:07:12,916 --> 00:07:15,000
Oh, yeah, they completely wiped
out "Samantha" and "Paramount"!

170
00:07:15,083 --> 00:07:16,125
[KAIDOU]
Whoa, I can't believe you know

171
00:07:16,208 --> 00:07:17,875
about "Samantha" and
"Paramount," too!

172
00:07:17,958 --> 00:07:19,458
[SAIKI]
Quite the coincidence.

173
00:07:19,541 --> 00:07:22,250
[KUBOYASU] Glad I finally found
somebody with common interests.

174
00:07:22,333 --> 00:07:23,958
